{\*\generator Msftedit 5.41.15.1515;}\viewkind4\uc1\pard\cf1\b\f0\fs20 In this example, you can re-sort the data in several different ways. These options are also available within the program, just as they are for other Data sources. Since XML files are typically rather small, there is not a lot of overhead for sorting the data any way you need to.\par
